> >Just a trivial question here( maybe a couple)
> >Were there one year only parts in the 68?
>
> - padded dash board raised above the instrument cluster;
> - rear view mirror;
> - door handles (64-68);
> - windshield wiper arms;
> - i have a set of seemingly 68 only front bumper overriders,
>   have seen matching overriders, larger, on a local 68 westy;
> - master cylinder fill res., and metal line to m/c;
> - idiot lights have no symbols.
>
> Q: do 69 up double cabs have grey weave seatbelts with the crest decal
>      on a metal clasp, or is that 68 only?
